{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726", "id": 377967010, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNzc5NjcwMTA=", "number": 55726, "title": "std::io::Result<()> is twice as big as it should be", "user": {"login": "gnzlbg", "id": 904614, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjkwNDYxNA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/904614?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg", "html_url": "https://github.com/gnzlbg", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2018-11-06T18:01:10Z", "updated_at": "2018-11-06T19:36:17Z", "closed_at": "2018-11-06T19:36:00Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "```rust\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let s = std::mem::size_of::<std::io::Result<()>>(); \r\n    println!(\"{}\", s);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nreturns 16 on the playground, but on `x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu` AFAICT `std::io::Result<()>` is either `Ok` if the error code is zero, or an `Err` if the error code is not-zero. That means that it should have the same size as `c_int`.\r\n\r\nThe problem appears to be that the `Error` type can be zero. It has three variants:\r\n\r\n* `Os(i32)`  [here](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/9653f790333d1270f36f1614e85d8a7b54193e75/src/libstd/io/error.rs#L78) should probably be `Os(NonZero<i32>)` at least on unixes, \r\n* `ErrorKind` [here](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/9653f790333d1270f36f1614e85d8a7b54193e75/src/libstd/io/error.rs#L101) can be zero, but maybe we can avoid this by giving the variants values that are not zero?\r\n* `Box<...>` is never null, so there is nothing to do here.\r\n\r\nIf there is a way to ensure that `Error` is never zero, then we can fix this issue. ", "closed_by": {"login": "gnzlbg", "id": 904614, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjkwNDYxNA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/904614?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg", "html_url": "https://github.com/gnzlbg", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gnzlbg/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/55726/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "http